ISO Audit Sample Data Cc NonPrivilegedpst Chris We are planning to use the following days to gather data for the ISO audit Februay June July August December No data is taken from due to the conversion from CHEOPS to MDMA The days represent high UFE days from each quarter of see ISO analysis July and August were included on the resubmittal analysis you provided December is an exit sample from the audit period Please respond with any concerns or comments Thanks Ken

Sample Data RequestNonPrivilegedpst Chris We have contacted Pat Priestley regarding obtaining the following data for the ISO audit We requested two sets of data One set which includes daily detail source data from a sample of meters before the application of distribution loss factors and load profiles and a second set which includes the daily detail meter data that is summed within the SQMD file For each UDC we requested data from meters from each rate class actual meter and estimated meter In addition we requested Enron meters from each UDC from different rate classes The meter data should be taken from respectively Pat has notified us that a WIP is required in order for us to obtain this data please confirm if this is the case Regards Ken
